org.eclipse.lyo.client.oslc

Class OslcClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.lyo.client.oslc.OslcClient
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JazzFormAuthClient, OslcOAuthClient

    public class OslcClient
extends Object
    An OSLC Client. Provides an Apache HttpClient, an Apache Wink REST ClientConfig and defines a getResource method which returns an Apache Wink ClientResponse.
